【重口注意】繁育：夺命舰罗浮
仙舟联盟之一的罗浮在了某一天开始突然失去了对外界的联系，陆陆续续有势力尝试登陆调查，但无一幸免的都失去了讯息，传言已经陨落的繁育星神塔伊兹育罗斯在这里找到了新的母体，迎来了复活。
已知：有个缺乏常识的生命科学家拿着不明不白的危险玩意爆改了个人形生物丢到星际飞船上去了，会发生什么不用我多说了吧。（其实本来是打算万圣节那天发的，但是后来话锋一转魅魔白枪呆了，翻文件夹才把这玩意翻出来，泪目）

【Attention】 Breeding: The Deadly Ship Luofu
Luofu, one of the Fairy Boat Alliance, suddenly lost contact with the outside world one day. Forces continued to try to land and investigate, but none of them were spared and lost information. Rumor has it that the fallen breeding star god Taizyurus found a new mother body here and was resurrected.
Known: A life scientist lacking common sense took an unknown and dangerous gadget, transformed a human form, and threw it onto a starship. I don't need to explain what would happen. ( Actually, I originally planned to post this on Halloween, but then the tone turned and Succubus White Gun was stunned. I dug through the folders and finally found this thing. Tears welled up in my eyes.)
